Predict Missing Values Transformation: Fill In Missing Values

In CRM Analytics, use the Predict Missing Values transformation in a Data Prep recipe to complete your data by filling in missing values in a text column. CRM Analytics Intelligently predicts values based on values in other strongly correlated columns in your data.

To create a Predict Missing Values transformation:

* Select up to three text columns to use to predict missing values
* Each column must have less than 200 unique values and contain clean, quality data
* Use the bucket transformation to bucket field values with the same meaning if needed

Run the recipe to generate predictions. You can view the dataset as a values table to see the predictions.

Limitations:

* If there aren't enough rows to make accurate predictions, CRM Analytics doesn't insert predicted values.
* Recipes that predict values can take longer to run.
title: Predicting Missing Values in Data Prep
